title: Consultation App
description: Mobile application connecting users with expert consultants. Features real-time chat and appointment scheduling.

body.raw:
# Overview

Developed a cross-platform mobile application using **React Native**. this app solves the problem of finding reliable consultants quickly.

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend**: React Native, React Navigation.
- **Backend**: Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Storage).
- **State Management**: Redux Toolkit.
